Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 以世界為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥 戰鬥 不停戰鬥的黑色勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於真正崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色勇者被守護世界的女神們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印在南端的遙遠盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那裡還住著另一個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太過醜陋 無比孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨得快要死掉的寂寞惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能將你的身體給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃掉你的半邊身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你 我的身體根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被稱為「所有公式」的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便分成了「解開所有公式者」和「編造所有公式者」兩部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而勇者立刻吃掉了「編造所有公式者」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者將世界不斷破壞 破壞 破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到達了其中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那裡只有漆黑的絕望 痛楚 孤獨 地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}抬头仰望追忆之门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及黑暗 黑暗 黑暗 黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:03.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}聴いていた遠い囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:03.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}远处传来似曾相识的低语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:09.02,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}導いて魂の迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:09.02,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}指引我去往灵魂的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想破壞整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.53,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}ひとひらの光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.53,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}走上那一线光明之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻要在這之前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來代替我承受這黑暗和痛楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.75,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}つらぬく痛みはInnocent Trick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.75,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}痛彻心扉的是无辜的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我剩下的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.25,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.25,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}我相信自己并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將黑暗放進這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:28.62,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}此処は彷徨いのParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:28.62,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}此处是彷徨的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:34.56,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:34.56,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}展开将心染上纯白的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的惡魔 並沒感到有多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:41.30,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:41.30,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}若能映入你的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為即使只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為朋友而活過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.87,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}微笑って抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.87,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}请微笑着抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:50.70,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}生まれてきた意味を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:50.70,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}了解诞生的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的惡魔 是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:58.69,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}見つめ合って創まるよ Destiny Regend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:58.69,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}彼此凝望 去开创命运的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最後 也是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那傢伙好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人叫來自己卻不在是怎麼回事 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉烏前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們被叫來的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}遠去時日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看起來像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你接下來打算把我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道有一天會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始覺得事情會好轉 可以一直持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就總是會突然變成這種局面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想殺了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在你手下 或許也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能被你殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊 就算我這種人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也有個傻瓜會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經答應她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能殺我的人已經定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲莉絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打破約定的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是把你當成摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是要殺我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定決定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束一切吧 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還結束不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏 上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求…雷鳴 電光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切都是我下令研製的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這個國家幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 很普通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只選擇了一些必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說因為必要就進行了人體實驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底背負了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要一個人背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我幫不了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你還把我當外人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是摯友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊 席恩·阿斯塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴 電光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不會放棄的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你牛角尖鑽得多深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何陷入黑暗 無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不會放棄你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你殺害同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走吧 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救出哭成這樣的你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的決定果然是正確的 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救你 無論世界變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的摯愛 寂寞的惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你 我才拔出了劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了嗎 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠 在永遠的地獄徘徊的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將你送去那裡 送去 送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰 α嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是α吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將化為「真」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「編造所有公式者」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會做到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有點輕視你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快制止他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是很想吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在還不到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵的他還是這種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣改變不了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括他 也包括你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還包括你最重視的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你似乎還留有一點理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理智？你竟然會說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想看看你身上的理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 席恩不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕不會失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我選擇了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他總是會選擇正確的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩會背叛你 萊納·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋的野獸 悲哀的惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你就繼續玩你的友情遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂他心中苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打著無聊的正義和愛的旗幟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一如既往地睡你的安穩覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡啦 快起床 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡糊塗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 讓我幫你幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己卻先陣亡了 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡著了嗎 睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四小時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些都是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實 好像做了很…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的剛才我還記著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像是很令人不快的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還好我把你叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 幫大忙了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說了什麼「被熟女的胸罩包圍我真是太幸福了」之類的夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還一直猶豫著要不要叫醒你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘了 我的愛好洩底了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃不…你這麼爽快就承認了 真是一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就繼續工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你給我上床好好睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你一個人把那些全解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛不叫醒我而自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 因為我叫你也不醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 囉嗦囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別管了 快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 睡了四小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以和你繼續工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺 殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在此殺掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納就連死都死不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會永遠…在地獄裡徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我要 把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從黑暗裡救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺不了這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有人贏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我們好脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要將朋友當做祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打進地獄 再向前進？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可我是連殺萊納…救萊納都做不到的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再苛責自己了 你的選擇沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你不必再苦惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 接下來我會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人 這裡禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 結果那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒殺我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 看守大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問你點事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不在就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出一副那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾獻上契約之文…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…幹什麼？我還想問你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說…你真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…找了好久 一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩說的話我也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在找 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過席恩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他變得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑著說他殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得像要哭出來似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你不可能殺萊納的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他 還是一直笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我不要再去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也別跟他扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他向奈爾法皇國出兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率領用禁忌之術創造的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將奈爾法人民全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國人民都為他而狂熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他是英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要統治世界的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都瘋了 大家都瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩 大家 整個國家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再擔心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄王 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們逃了 追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了又怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找 阻止他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去揭開真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安逃掉啊 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著也跟死了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:36.73,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:36.73,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}那一天已忘却的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能留在人身邊 也不能愛別人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:42.69,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:42.69,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}在天空彼方隐隐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就放棄了一切生存意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:50.77,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:50.77,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心灵原本应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從心底被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:58.25,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}震えた瞳は応えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:58.25,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}颤抖的瞳眸却无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:11.28,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:11.28,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}这声音你已无法听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求燒原·紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:16.07,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:16.07,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:20.93,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}全てをこの身体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:20.93,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}一一铭刻于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃色的頭髮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:26.04,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:26.04,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就从此地 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.72,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.72,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}记忆的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想回報你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:35.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}今絡まる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:35.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}解开此刻交缠的命运丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 現在雖然不知道你深陷什麼困境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.94,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.94,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我會去到你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}若能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:51.55,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もっと守れるように 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:51.55,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}定能守护你 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此不知道需要多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要的我都會弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好覺悟等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:12.12,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}解き放つたくさんの願いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:12.12,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}被解放的眾多心願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你後悔那時沒有殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:17.95,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}空の向こう 廣がる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:17.95,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}向著天空盡頭蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一個人擅自陷入絕望 背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要哭泣的你 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:26.45,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心まで重なっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:26.45,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}連心靈都應早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認你有一個最棒的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:33.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}震えた瞳が遠くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:33.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}顫抖的瞳眸卻已遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.80,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに失っても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.80,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也會前進的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.16,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに通り過ぎても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.16,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:46.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}何度でも探すから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:46.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}多少次我都會去尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放棄你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.05,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}果てなきフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.05,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}無盡的Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}闇を切り裂く程の力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}足以劃破黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:01.40,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}手の中に摑んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:01.40,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}我已握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.97,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}二人のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.97,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}兩人的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.30,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もう誰かを傷付けたりせずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.30,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}已不想再傷害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}生きて行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}這樣生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:19.35,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}前よりも真っ直ぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:19.35,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}想比以前更坦率地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:26.48,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}見つめたいから 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:26.48,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:53.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もう一度 呼び合って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:53.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}再一次彼此呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:58.18,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:58.18,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:03.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}全てをこの身體に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:03.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}一一銘刻於此身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:08.33,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}步き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:08.33,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就從此地 邁出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:12.00,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}二人のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:12.00,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}兩人的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:17.46,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}今 どんな痛みも越えて行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:17.46,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如今只要跨越所有痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:24.23,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}強くなれる また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:24.23,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就能變得堅強 若能再重逢
